OL,3,CCost of new drugs 'do not always
OL,4,Cjustify the benefits', researchers warn
OL,6,FOffsetting NHS funding from existing
OL,7,Fservices to pay for expensive new
OL,8,Fdrugs could be harming the health of
OL,9,Fthe nation, a study suggests.
OL,11,FThe cost of innovative new medicines
OL,12,F"do not always justify the benefits
OL,13,Fthey offer", researchers warned.
OL,15,FThey suggest England's pharmaceutical
OL,16,Fpricing policy should be reformed "to
OL,17,Fbetter serve the health needs" of all
OL,18,FNHS patients.
