OL,3,CCost of new drugs 'do not always
OL,4,Cjustify the benefits', researchers warn
OL,6,FHowever, NHS spending watchdog the
OL,7,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,8,FExcellence (Nice) said its role is
OL,9,F"vital", with it helping to prevent a
OL,10,F"postcode lottery" in patient access
OL,11,Fand potentially higher costs.
OL,13,FThe study, led by academics at the
OL,14,FLondon School of Economics and
OL,15,FPolitical Science (LSE), looked at how
OL,16,Fmany additional years of full health
OL,17,Fwere generated by drugs approved by
OL,18,FNice between 2000 and 2020.
