OL,3,CCost of new drugs 'do not always
OL,4,Cjustify the benefits', researchers warn
OL,6,FThe analysis found new medicines led
OL,7,Fto 3.75 million additional years of
OL,8,Ffull health, costing #75 billion.
OL,10,FHowever, it suggests that redirecting
OL,11,Fthat funding to existing services
OL,12,Fcould have generated five million
OL,13,Fyears of full health.
