OL,3,CCost of new drugs 'do not always
OL,4,Cjustify the benefits', researchers warn
OL,6,F"However, innovative drugs are
OL,7,Fexpensive, and their costs do not
OL,8,Falways justify the benefits they
OL,9,Foffer."
OL,11,FAcademics said the findings relate to
OL,12,FNice's cost-effectiveness threshold
OL,13,Fand suggest it should be lowered.
OL,15,FNice advises its committees to
OL,16,Fconsider new drugs as offering value
OL,17,Ffor money to the NHS if they cost less
OL,18,Fthan #20,000 to #30,000 per additional
OL,19,Fyear of full health gained.
