OL,3,CCost of new drugs 'do not always
OL,4,Cjustify the benefits', researchers warn
OL,6,FIrene Papanicolas, professor of health
OL,7,Fservices, policy and practice at Brown
OL,8,FUniversity, said the findings,
OL,9,Fpublished in The Lancet, "are
OL,10,Freflective of the tight budget of the
OL,11,FNHS".
OL,13,F"In this environment, offsetting
OL,14,Ffunding from existing services to pay
OL,15,Fhigh prices for new drugs can more
OL,16,Fadversely affect population health
OL,17,Fthan in health systems where there is
OL,18,Fgreater budgetary flexibility," she
OL,19,Fadded.
