OL,6,FBeth Woods, senior research fellow at
OL,7,FCentre for Health Economics at
OL,8,FUniversity of York, said: "This work
OL,9,Fshows that there is a need to reform
OL,10,Fpharmaceutical pricing policy in
OL,11,FEngland to better serve the health
OL,12,Fneeds of all patients served by the
OL,13,FNHS."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Nice said the
OL,16,Fspending watchdog's role is "vital"
OL,17,Fand helps prevent a postcode lottery.
