OL,3,CCost of new drugs 'do not always
OL,4,Cjustify the benefits', researchers warn
OL,6,F"Spending money on new medicines does
OL,7,Fcreate an opportunity cost, displacing
OL,8,Fservices elsewhere in the health
OL,9,Fsystem," they said.
OL,11,F"That's why Nice's role is vital: we
OL,12,Fcarefully evaluate new treatments and
OL,13,Frecommend only those that offer value-
OL,14,Ffor-money for the taxpayer.
OL,16,F"This is especially important during
OL,17,Ftimes of significant challenge to the
OL,18,FNHS. Every pound of the NHS budget can
OL,19,Fonly be spent once.
