OL,3,CCost of new drugs 'do not always
OL,4,Cjustify the benefits', researchers warn
OL,6,F"If Nice had not recommended these
OL,7,Finnovative new medicines, they almost
OL,8,Fcertainly would have been used within
OL,9,Fthe NHS anyway.
OL,11,F"Without Nice's input, funding
OL,12,Fdecisions would be taken locally,
OL,13,Fleading to inequitable patient access
OL,14,F` the 'postcode lottery' ` and
OL,15,Fpotentially higher costs, because
OL,16,Fmultiple local negotiations with
OL,17,Fpharmaceutical companies may not drive
OL,18,Fbest value for the NHS."
